{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_0","type":"agent_message","text":"# Implementation Notes\n## Decisions Made\n- Generalized `agent_execution` so it is no longer coupled only to workflows, using an `InvocationContract` enum.\n- Added a full `requirements_drafting` bounded context covering model, contracts, renderers, and service layers.\n- Implemented four CLI commands: `draft`, `quick`, `show`, and `answer`.\n- Added `FsRequirementsStore` with seed rollback semantics.\n- Wrote implementation notes to `20260312-loop10-impl-notes.md`.\n\n## Spec Deviations\n- No material spec deviations were introduced.\n- The delivered scope included 13 modified files and 7 newly created files.\n\n## Testing\n- 272 tests pass total: 248 existing and 24 new.\n- Added 24 unit tests.\n- Added 10 Gherkin conformance scenarios.\n- Resolved unused imports so compilation completes with zero warnings."}}
